I've been to this place several times before. All previous trips have been pleasurable. I was in the building and decided to stop by. I got the bourbon chicken, jambalaya, Mac and cheese and cabbage. Upon getting home I began to eat. The bourbon chicken was good. Jambalaya was spicy. Mac and cheese was bland and the cabbage had too much pepper. I put the container to the side. Hours later there was this stench. After searching for it. It was the food. The cabbage to be exact as that was the only thing left. It smelled as if it had spoiled and was giving off a rotten smell. I had to tie it in three bags and take it to the garbage can. Early the next morning I was violently I'll. This was the only food I ate the day before and I had yet to eat anything else. Health inspector needs to visit this place
